features: 💝【EASY INSTALLATION】 The screen protector is specially designed for iPhone 14/ iPhone 13/ iPhone 13 Pro 6.1 inch screen, 100% touch accurate. It's a three-pack and comes with an auto-alignment installation frame for effortless adhesion. Super easy to install!

💯【USER-FRIENDLY DESIGN】 The open edge design does not in any way disrupt images of the front camera and as a result does NOT interfere with Face ID. The iPhone 14/13/13 Pro tempered glass is designed to be a little smaller than the actual screen, providing just the right fit and compatibility for your phone cases.

💪【ANTI-SCRATCH & IMPACT PROTECTION】 UNBREAKcable iPhone 14/13/13 Pro glass screen protector is made with reinforced technology. The tempered glass protector can effectively protect your iPhone from unwanted scuffs and scratches by knife, keys and some other hard substances.

💧【BUBBLE-FREE & ANTI-FINGERPRINT】 The iPhone 14/13/13 Pro tempered glass screen protector will self-expel air bubble when automatically bonding with the screen. Coated with hydrophobic and oleophobic clear layers on the glass protector can against oil residue from fingerprints from long-term use.

💎【99.99% HD CLEAR】 Ultra-thin and ultra-clear material makes it retain amazing clarity for viewing experience. High-quality design and engineering, durable tempered glass to deliver the brightness, sharpness, and detail you expect from your phone screen. The visual experience is comparable to the device itself because of the crystal-clear protective layer.

🎁【WHAT YOU GET】UNBREAKcable Shatterproof Tempered Glass 3 pack, Easy Installation frame, 3 wet wipes, 3 dust absorbers, 4 dust stickers, lint-free cloth, detailed installation guide, 36-month warranty and easy-to-reach customer service at no additional cost. UNBREAKcable Support Team is always stand by your side to help.

Super easy installation, 9H hardness, Shatterproof, Shockproof, Anti-scratches, Anti-fingerprints, HD(99.99% transparency), and bubble-free, etc. These features make the UNBREAKcable screen protector the best shield for your iPhone 14/13/13 pro screen. How drop-resistant are our UNBREAKcable iPhone 14 / 13 / 13 Pro screen protectors? Every single piece of the UNBREAKcable iPhone 14 screen protector/ iPhone 13/13 Pro screen protector has passed a 9H pencil test and a 10.4 kg / 23 lbs pressure test. Frequently Asked Questions Q1: What is the specialty of this screen protector compared with much cheaper ones? A1: Our screen protector made with superior 9H tempered glass is highly durable and scratch-resistant, reinforced to be twice as strong as other ordinary tempered films on the market. 10s Super-easy Installed Auto Alignment Kit makes your installation easier than ever. This screen protector utilizes automatic adsorption technology to ensure that no bubbles can exist during the installation process. Q2: How can I get rid of bubbles? reviews.reviewText: Will not purchase anything else but these for my fruit phones! These have worked flawlessly and are super easy to install. reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 6, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Cracked in a day but New ones work great!
reviews.reviewText: Update to review:The company sent us new protectors since I’m guessing our previous protectors were maybe faulty. We have had new protectors on for about a week now with no issues. Installation was easy like last time and no issues since then. We did have one protector from the previous package that is still functioning great with no issues, so I’m guessing the other two must have had issues in manufacturing. The company was great to work with and I would totally recommend them and buy from them again.Previous review:We were so excited for an “Unbreakable” screen protector. Got them yesterday and installed last night. By noon today my phone has a huge crack through it! I haven’t dropped it and it has been in my pocket most of the day. My pockets are baggy and not in my back pocket, so didn’t sit on it or anything. So disappointing!We got a pack of 3 screen protectors for 3 new phones. Mine protector broke and another protector didn’t stick around the edges, so only one is still working correctly. Such a bummer. Installing the protector was an easy process, similar to most protectors… but I did like this process a little better than the cheaper ones we’ve used in the past. Which is why I gave it more stars than only one.
